item.title: Colourful Player Numbers on Caps for MLB’s 2024 Players’ Weekend
item.description: Next weekend is Players’ Weekend across Major League Baseball. The series of games played from August 16-18 will be the first time MLB will host a Players’ Weekend since 2019. As part of this year’s celebration, each player’s uniform number will be worn on the right side of their cap

item.title: Illinois Unveils 1924 Throwback Uniforms For Memorial Stadium Rededication
item.description: The Illinois football program announced on Wednesday that it will wear 1924 throwback uniforms against Michigan on Oct. 19 to mark the 100th anniversary of Memorial Stadium’s dedication and rededication that afternoon. The uniforms were designed to mirror what the Fighting Illini wore against the Wolverines on Oct. 18, 1924,
